<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>공공재 메인페이지</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/sidebar.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main(LogO).css" />
  <link rel="icon" href="/images/reallogo 1.png" type="image/png" />
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <!-- ✅ 사이드바 삽입 -->
    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div class="logo-area">
        <a href="/main">
          <img src="/images/reallogo 1.png" alt="공공재 로고" class="logo" />
        </a>
      </div>

      <nav>
        <ul class="menu">
          <li class="active">
            <a href="/main" class="menu-item">
              <div class="left">
                <img src="/images/Home_Blue.png" class="icon" alt="홈" />
                <span>홈</span>
              </div>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="dropdown">
            <div class="menu-item dropdown-toggle">
              <div class="left">
                <img src="/images/Trophy.png" class="icon" alt="공모전" />
                <span>공모전 페이지</span>
              </div>
              <img src="/images/toggle.png" class="arrow-icon" />
            </div>
            <ul class="submenu">
  <li><a href="/contest" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">공모전 정보</a></li>
  <li><a href="/recruit" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">공모전 팀원 모집</a></li>
</ul>

          </li>
          <li>
  <a href="/portfolio/<%= user.id %>" class="menu-item">
    <div class="left">
      <img src="/images/human.png" class="icon" alt="포트폴리오" />
      <span>나의 포트폴리오</span>
    </div>
  </a>
</li>
          <li class="dropdown">
            <div class="menu-item dropdown-toggle">
              <div class="left">
                <img src="/images/Group_human.png" class="icon" alt="커뮤니티" />
                <span>커뮤니티</span>
              </div>
              <img src="/images/toggle.png" class="arrow-icon" />
            </div>
            <ul class="submenu">
              <li><a href="/community" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">커뮤니티</a></li>
  <li><a href="/community?category=스터디원 모집" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">스터디원 모집</a></li>
  <li><a href="/community?category=Q%26A" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">Q&A</a></li>
  <li><a href="/community?category=공모전 후기" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">공모전 후기</a></li>
</ul>

          </li>
          <li class="timer-menu">
            <div class="menu-item">
              <div class="left">
                <img id="timerIcon" src="/images/Timer.png" class="icon" alt="타이머" />
                <span id="timerText">타이머</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timer-layout">
              <div class="timer-blocks">
                <div class="time-group">
                  <div class="time-cell" id="hourTens">0</div>
                  <div class="time-cell" id="hourOnes">0</div>
                </div>
                <div class="colon">:</div>
                <div class="time-group">
                  <div class="time-cell" id="minuteTens">0</div>
                  <div class="time-cell" id="minuteOnes">0</div>
                </div>
                <div class="colon">:</div>
                <div class="time-group">
                  <div class="time-cell" id="secondTens">0</div>
                  <div class="time-cell" id="secondOnes">0</div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="timer-controls">
                <input type="text" class="keyword-input" placeholder="키워드" />
                <div class="timer-buttons">
                  <button class="start-btn"><img src="/images/Play.png" alt="시작" /></button>
                  <button class="stop-btn"><img src="/images/Stop circle.png" alt="정지" /></button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </nav>

      <div class="recent-section">
        <div class="recent-title">최근 학습</div>
        <div class="recent-graph" id="recentGraph"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="logout-section">
        <button class="logout-btn" aria-label="로그아웃">
          <img src="/images/logOut.png" class="logout-icon" />
          로그아웃
        </button>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <!-- ✅ 본문 콘텐츠 -->
    <main class="main-content">
      <div class="intro-area">
        <div class="intro-text">
          <h1>같이 도전하는 공모전,<br>공공재와 함께 시작하세요</h1>
          <p>팀원 모집, 스터디 구성, 공모전 정보까지.<br>공공전을 시작하는 가장 쉬운 방법, 공공재에서 함께하세요.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="main-logo">
          <img src="/images/reallogo 1.png" alt="공공재 메인 로고">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="buttons">
        <div class="buttons">
  <button class="btn main-btn" onclick="location.href='/contest'">공모전 참여하기</button>
  <button class="btn main-btn" onclick="location.href='/community?category=스터디원 모집'">스터디 참여하기</button>

</div>

      </div>
    </main>
  </div>

  <script src="/js/sidebar.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
